OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUrgent talks held over BBC 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstar allegations           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Culture Secretary Lucy Frazer has held 
OL,6, urgent talks with the BBC's director   
OL,7, general after a presenter was accused  
OL,8, of paying a teenager for sexually      
OL,9, explicit photos.                       
OL,11,FTim Davie assured her the corporation  
OL,12,Fwas investigating the claims "swiftly  
OL,13,Fand sensitively", the minister said.   
OL,15,FThe allegations, first reported by the 
OL,16,FSun, include that the young person's   
OL,17,Ffamily complained to the BBC in May.   
OL,19,FThe paper says it is not naming the    
OL,20,Fpresenter for legal reasons.           
